metadata.name: HAPPY GIRL
metadata.description:
Her name is Misaki. She's a high school girl.
She is cute. That's why she often confesses her love to me.

" I love you, Misaki. Will you go out with me? "

The person who told her this was a senior whom she admired.
Of course, there was no reason to refuse.

"I love you too!"

When she said that, she was without a doubt the happiest person in the world.
